name: Rain Forest Pebble Stone Collection - Grey Beach Pebbles
description: Margo Garden Products Beach Pebble collection offers hand-picked stones from the most beautiful beaches in the world. This 30 lb. bag is easy to tote and store for adding a beautiful and long lasting accent to your landscape and design.
